Revision history for Perinci-Sub-Property-dies_on_error

0.05     2014-03-07 (SHARYANTO)

         - Adjust to Perinci::Sub::Wrapper 0.51.

         - Now cannot be used when result_naked=>1.

         - Propagate error from eval block in generated wrapper code
           ($_w_eval_err).


0.04     2012-12-21 (SHARYANTO)

         - No functional changes. Use Perinci::Sub::PropertyUtil.


0.03     2012-08-09 (SHARYANTO)

         - No functional changes. Correct casing in name:
           Perinci::Sub::{p,P}roperty::


0.02     2012-07-31 (SHARYANTO)

         - No functional changes. Show function name in die message.


0.01     2012-07-31 (SHARYANTO)

         - First release.
